  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Hand][Main] If you have a Digimon with [Justimon] or [Raidenmon]
    in its name in play, you may pay 1 memory to place this card under that Digimon
    as its bottom digivolution card.[When Digivolving] You may trash 1 Digimon card
    with [Machine] or [Cyborg] in its traits in your hand to place 1 of your opponent\u2019s
    level 4 or lower Digimon at the bottom of its owner's deck."
  InheritedEffectDiscription_JPN: "\u3010\u30A2\u30BF\u30C3\u30AF\u6642\u3011Lv.4\u4EE5\u4E0B\u306E\u76F8\u624B\u306E\u30C7\u30B8\u30E2\u30F31\u4F53\u3092\u624B\u672D\u306B\u623B\u3059\u3002"
  InheritedEffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Attacking] Return 1 of your opponent\u2019s
    level 4 or lower Digimon to its owner\u2019s hand."
